Speaking of nice features: How much work/how difficult would it be to add the "How would you like to fix it (for a "begin and end block")" for missing Packages, allowing to add
import Pkg; Pkg.add(["firstmissingpkg", "secondmissingpck"])
with one click? I can't be the only one thinking about that (always trying to optimize recurrent tasks, and this is one for me).

